In 1948, Olympiacos played 14 regional games with minor clubs from Piraeus and 4 with the champions of Athens and Thessaloniki. Same thing in 1955. It was not a nationwide round robin league competition. A team from Crete for example could not participate. Thank you

message: National League was etsablished in 1959-60. Ranking statistics or seasons in top division cannot include seasons from 1927 to 1959 simply because the league format was not the same each year. For example for many years only teams from Athens, Piraeus and Thessaloniki qualified for the final phase. A team like OFI Crete or Panachaiki could not participate and it is not fair in my opinion to have statistics before 1959. Thank you
